title: The Queen of England: Ascension
description: With stunning revelations carrying over from her past, how will Queen Juliette move forward? Beginning with defending London from a terrible sea creature, the regent has her work cut out for her in the exciting conclusion of The Queen of England series. As the New World Order threatens her shores, will she choose love or duty? Family or her crown? With a team of friends and family to support her, Juliette and Excalibur face off on a final mission to secure her rightful throne.The Queen of England: Ascension is the final book in The Queen of England trilogy by Courtney Brandt. Don't miss the first novel, The Queen of England: Coronation or the second book, The Queen of England: Grand Tour which are both already available.
author: Courtney Brandt
